# LINE Flex Message JSON Template

This repository contains a sample JSON template for a LINE Flex Message. The template is designed to create a rich bubble message with an image, title, rating stars, and contact information.

## JSON Template

The JSON template can be used to create a Flex Message bubble in LINE's Messaging API. Below is a brief description of the JSON structure.

